 101:Core/Src/port.c **** /* Let the user override the default SysTick clock rate.  If defined by the
 102:Core/Src/port.c ****  * user, this symbol must equal the SysTick clock rate when the CLK bit is 0 in the
 103:Core/Src/port.c ****  * configuration register. */
